reviewText: Perfect, Is everything i was looking for. Thank you so much. I'm in love with this movies. Will recommended for any who wants to watch on how Pablo Leon Jaramillo started with the drug dealing, etc.

A year or so ago, I bought the first season of this production. There is now a second season, and I bought this thinking that was it. It turns out that they split the first season in several boxes, and now they have one box labeled Part 2. I bought something I already haven because the item description was totally misleading.
